          <div class="mt-5 prose prose-indigo text-gray-500">
            <ul class="list-disc">
              <li>This involves fasting for 24 hours, once or twice a week, for example by not eating from dinner one
                day until dinner the next day.</li><br>

            </ul>
          </div>

